sequenceDiagram
    participant A as User A
    participant B as User B

    Note over A,B: Both start with "Hello"

    A->>A: Insert("!", pos=5)<br/>→ "Hello!"
    B->>B: Insert(" World", pos=5)<br/>→ "Hello World"

    Note over A,B: Exchange operations

    B-->>A: Insert(" World", pos=5)
    Note over A: Transform: pos 5→6<br/>(A already inserted at 5)
    A->>A: Apply Insert(" World", pos=6)<br/>→ "Hello! World"

    A-->>B: Insert("!", pos=5)
    Note over B: Transform: pos 5→5<br/>(no shift needed)
    B->>B: Apply Insert("!", pos=5)<br/>→ "Hello! World"

    Note over A,B: Both converge to "Hello! World" ✅
